Brazil 2002 Cup

(Atlético (PR), Flamengo (RJ), Grêmio (RS) and São Caetano (SP) didn't play
due to their participation in Copa Libertadores]

Obs.: 1) In each match, the second mentioned team plays the 2nd leg in home.
      2) Away goal rule applied on all phases.

